these veils misunderstanding,

00:12:27.550 --> 00:12:30.550 align:middle line:90%
misunderstanding.

00:12:30.550 --> 00:12:33.010 align:middle line:84%
Bit by bit, we feel less
more and more separate.

00:12:33.010 --> 00:12:36.250 align:middle line:84%
