00:38:20.950 --> 00:38:22.310 align:middle line:90%
Molecules are made of atoms.

00:38:22.310 --> 00:38:28.210 align:middle line:84%
Atoms are made of electrons and
whatever, subatomic particles.

00:38:28.210 --> 00:38:32.080 align:middle line:84%
And ultimately, physics seeks
to find a unified field which

00:38:32.080 --> 00:38:37.900 align:middle line:84%
would be sort of a single
constituent ultimate source

00:38:37.900 --> 00:38:41.260 align:middle line:84%
or foundation of the
universe and actually

00:38:41.260 --> 00:38:43.975 align:middle line:84%
has-- it has succeeded in
doing that to a great extent.

00:38:43.975 --> 00:39:01.220 align:middle line:90%


00:39:01.220 --> 00:39:04.480 align:middle line:84%
So creation appears
very diverse.

00:39:04.480 --> 00:39:06.190 align:middle line:90%
People appear very diverse.

00:39:06.190 --> 00:39:09.310 align:middle line:84%
Their opinions are
diverse and so on.

00:39:09.310 --> 00:39:11.080 align:middle line:84%
And diversity is
the spice of life.

00:39:11.080 --> 00:39:12.280 align:middle line:90%
Diversity is great.

00:39:12.280 --> 00:39:17.740 align:middle line:84%
But essentially, fundamentally,
all of this diversity

00:39:17.740 --> 00:39:20.290 align:middle line:90%
is just one thing.

00:39:20.290 --> 00:39:23.425 align:middle line:84%
We appear diverse, but we're
really all the same soul.

00:39:23.425 --> 00:39:24.550 align:middle line:90%
We're all the same essence.

00:39:24.550 --> 00:39:26.500 align:middle line:84%
We're all the same
consciousness,

00:39:26.500 --> 00:39:28.885 align:middle line:84%
and that means that there's
really only one of us.

00:39:28.885 --> 00:39:43.114 align:middle line:90%


00:39:43.114 --> 00:39:48.600 align:middle line:84%
>> I view humanity as all the
different people that make up

00:39:48.600 --> 00:39:53.490 align:middle line:84%
our world, is like individual
cells in this one cosmic body

00:39:53.490 --> 00:39:55.050 align:middle line:90%
of oneness.

00:39:55.050 --> 00:39:58.800 align:middle line:84%
And so yes, there's some
individuality there,

00:39:58.800 --> 00:40:03.360 align:middle line:84%
but there's a harmony
and interrelationship

00:40:03.360 --> 00:40:05.880 align:middle line:90%
between all people, really.

00:40:05.880 --> 00:40:07.455 align:middle line:90%
I'm you, and you're me.

00:40:07.455 --> 00:40:19.608 align:middle line:90%


00:40:19.608 --> 00:40:23.560 align:middle line:84%
>> I've heard people describe
the experience of unity

00:40:23.560 --> 00:40:27.020 align:middle line:84%
or unity consciousness, and
that's what I'm describing.

00:40:27.020 --> 00:40:30.040 align:middle line:84%
I'm describing a
unification of the inside

00:40:30.040 --> 00:40:34.810 align:middle line:84%
with the outside of this silent
levels of self-knowingness

00:40:34.810 --> 00:40:38.230 align:middle line:84%
with the regular
levels of my senses,

00:40:38.230 --> 00:40:42.010 align:middle line:84%
when I see stuff,
hear stuff, do stuff.

00:40:42.010 --> 00:40:44.830 align:middle line:90%
The outside is not the outside.

00:40:44.830 --> 00:40:46.960 align:middle line:90%
It's not separated from you.

00:40:46.960 --> 00:40:51.040 align:middle line:84%
It's a unification or
a see through, know

00:40:51.040 --> 00:40:53.980 align:middle line:90%
through oneness of experience.

00:40:53.980 --> 00:40:57.430 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:40:57.430 --> 00:42:36.930 align:middle line:90%


00:42:36.930 --> 00:42:39.560 align:middle line:84%
>> We're all on this
evolutionary train,

00:42:39.560 --> 00:42:40.460 align:middle line:90%
know it or not.

00:42:40.460 --> 00:42:43.610 align:middle line:84%
Now at a certain stage,
we begin to know it.

00:42:43.610 --> 00:42:46.010 align:middle line:84%
It becomes conscious
rather than just kind

00:42:46.010 --> 00:42:47.510 align:middle line:90%
of an automatic process.

00:42:47.510 --> 00:42:51.590 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes those
stages are abrupt.

00:42:51.590 --> 00:42:53.360 align:middle line:90%
Someone has a sudden awakening.

00:42:53.360 --> 00:42:56.330 align:middle line:84%
They might have been seeking
it, doing spiritual practices,

00:42:56.330 --> 00:42:58.550 align:middle line:84%
or they might just be tying
their shoes one morning

00:42:58.550 --> 00:43:00.830 align:middle line:84%
and all of a sudden,
boom, this shift

00:43:00.830 --> 00:43:02.450 align:middle line:90%
takes place in their awareness.

00:43:02.450 --> 00:43:04.410 align:middle line:84%
And they think,
whoa, what happened?

00:43:04.410 --> 00:43:06.870 align:middle line:90%
Where am I?

00:43:06.870 --> 00:43:10.640 align:middle line:84%
What I thought myself to
be I can no longer find,

00:43:10.640 --> 00:43:14.030 align:middle line:84%
and that can take a
long time to adjust to.

00:43:14.030 --> 00:43:16.820 align:middle line:84%
But I'd say that
most people don't

00:43:16.820 --> 00:43:20.900 align:middle line:84%
have these dramatic shifts that
take a long time to adjust to.

00:43:20.900 --> 00:43:22.220 align:middle line:90%
Some famous people do.

00:43:22.220 --> 00:43:23.240 align:middle line:90%
Eckhart Tolle did.

00:43:23.240 --> 00:43:27.590 align:middle line:84%
He was depressed and
even possibly suicidal.

00:43:27.590 --> 00:43:31.832 align:middle line:84%
And one night, he said, I can't
live with myself any longer.

00:43:31.832 --> 00:43:33.290 align:middle line:84%
And then he thought,
wait a minute.

00:43:33.290 --> 00:43:34.123 align:middle line:90%
Are there two of me?

00:43:34.123 --> 00:43:36.350 align:middle line:84%
Who is this self with
whom I cannot live?

00:43:36.350 --> 00:43:38.205 align:middle line:84%
And he woke up-- and
he went to sleep,

00:43:38.205 --> 00:43:40.580 align:middle line:84%
and he woke up in the morning
and everything had shifted.

00:43:40.580 --> 00:43:43.220 align:middle line:90%
And he never went back.

00:43:43.220 --> 00:43:46.250 align:middle line:84%
Many people aren't that
abrupt in their transition,

00:43:46.250 --> 00:43:52.280 align:middle line:84%
and they progress more
gradually and incrementally.

00:43:52.280 --> 00:44:04.016 align:middle line:90%


00:44:04.016 --> 00:44:09.440 align:middle line:84%
>> Awakening to non-separateness
actually requires certain

00:44:09.440 --> 00:44:11.130 align:middle line:90%
conditions.

00:44:11.130 --> 00:44:16.360 align:middle line:84%
It's very important to
find a copacetic map,

00:44:16.360 --> 00:44:19.400 align:middle line:84%
a map that suits
you in the moment

00:44:19.400 --> 00:44:21.980 align:middle line:90%
to take you to the next level.

00:44:21.980 --> 00:44:27.440 align:middle line:84%
And finding that map is
often another initiation.

00:44:27.440 --> 00:44:30.380 align:middle line:84%
I know there have been in
my life certain books I

00:44:30.380 --> 00:44:34.850 align:middle line:90%
read that felt so right.

00:44:34.850 --> 00:44:38.990 align:middle line:84%
Oh, I found myself
saying, why didn't anyone

00:44:38.990 --> 00:44:39.935 align:middle line:90%
ever tell me this?

00:44:39.935 --> 00:44:41.609 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:44:41.609 --> 00:44:46.240 align:middle line:90%


00:44:46.240 --> 00:44:50.770 align:middle line:84%
You have to have some kind
of guidance to the territory,

00:44:50.770 --> 00:44:52.660 align:middle line:90%
and that's very, very helpful.

00:44:52.660 --> 00:44:55.810 align:middle line:84%
You could find out on your
own by trial and error,

00:44:55.810 --> 00:44:57.670 align:middle line:84%
but you might find
out more quickly

00:44:57.670 --> 00:45:01.360 align:middle line:90%
by having an experienced guide.

00:45:01.360 --> 00:45:05.800 align:middle line:84%
And then next you need to
have a group of people.

00:45:05.800 --> 00:45:11.170 align:middle line:84%
I have discovered on my teaching
experience and my own awakening

00:45:11.170 --> 00:45:14.665 align:middle line:84%
that almost no one can awaken
absolutely on their own.

00:45:14.665 --> 00:45:23.820 align:middle line:90%


00:45:23.820 --> 00:45:27.030 align:middle line:84%
I once remember
in a group saying

00:45:27.030 --> 00:45:30.450 align:middle line:84%
to a person who was going
through an experience

00:45:30.450 --> 00:45:34.570 align:middle line:84%
of encountering illness
and distress about it

00:45:34.570 --> 00:45:36.180 align:middle line:90%
and speaking about it.

00:45:36.180 --> 00:45:40.020 align:middle line:84%
And I just suddenly felt,
oh, yeah, I know that.

00:45:40.020 --> 00:45:45.140 align:middle line:84%
She's myself who's suffering
a limit of her body mind.

00:45:45.140 --> 00:45:47.740 align:middle line:84%
>> So in order to
gain self-awareness,

00:45:47.740 --> 00:45:51.180 align:middle line:84%
you have to actually
do something.

00:45:51.180 --> 00:45:55.380 align:middle line:84%
You have to either meditate,
you have to do self-inquiry,

00:45:55.380 --> 00:45:57.310 align:middle line:90%
you have to go for it.

00:45:57.310 --> 00:46:00.370 align:middle line:84%
It's not going to
come all by itself.

00:46:00.370 --> 00:46:02.720 align:middle line:90%
You have to go for it.

00:46:02.720 --> 00:46:04.970 align:middle line:84%
I've meditated for
years and years.

00:46:04.970 --> 00:46:07.370 align:middle line:84%
I still meditate, and I
have this experience just

00:46:07.370 --> 00:46:08.690 align:middle line:90%
for-- because I enjoy it.

00:46:08.690 --> 00:46:11.280 align:middle line:90%


00:46:11.280 --> 00:46:13.830 align:middle line:90%
You're not a seeker for nothing.

00:46:13.830 --> 00:46:16.770 align:middle line:84%
A seeker means you're after
something, you want something,

00:46:16.770 --> 00:46:19.230 align:middle line:90%
you're going for it.

00:46:19.230 --> 00:46:22.156 align:middle line:84%
And if you have your own
way of doing that, fine.

00:46:22.156 --> 00:46:24.960 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, there are
techniques and procedures

00:46:24.960 --> 00:46:28.575 align:middle line:84%
that you can use to
enhance your experience.

00:46:28.575 --> 00:46:33.970 align:middle line:84%
>> I can just sit here
like this and meditate,

00:46:33.970 --> 00:46:35.260 align:middle line:90%
just no one would even know.

00:46:35.260 --> 00:46:37.585 align:middle line:84%
I could do it on a plane
or train or whatever.

00:46:37.585 --> 00:46:40.780 align:middle line:84%
>> There are teachers, there are
teachings, there are practices,

00:46:40.780 --> 00:46:44.890 align:middle line:84%
there are methods which anybody
can do which will enable

00:46:44.890 --> 00:46:48.220 align:middle line:84%
people, anyone, to start
experiencing these things

00:46:48.220 --> 00:46:49.050 align:middle line:90%
for themselves.

00:46:49.050 --> 00:47:32.455 align:middle line:90%


00:47:32.455 --> 00:47:34.360 align:middle line:84%
>> So you develop
self-awareness,

00:47:34.360 --> 00:47:36.910 align:middle line:84%
it has a quality of
silence and expansion,

00:47:36.910 --> 00:47:38.450 align:middle line:90%
and everybody can have that.

00:47:38.450 --> 00:47:41.440 align:middle line:84%
But then when you
begin to experience

00:47:41.440 --> 00:47:43.660 align:middle line:84%
that silence and
its expressions,

00:47:43.660 --> 00:47:45.980 align:middle line:84%
it gets very different
for everybody.

00:47:45.980 --> 00:47:49.630 align:middle line:84%
Some people only they
sense pure consciousness.

00:47:49.630 --> 00:47:51.130 align:middle line:90%
They don't see it.

00:47:51.130 --> 00:47:53.470 align:middle line:84%
Some people hear
some reverberation

00:47:53.470 --> 00:47:55.090 align:middle line:84%
and they say, well,
I can hear it.

00:47:55.090 --> 00:47:58.240 align:middle line:90%
It's beautiful, this sound.

00:47:58.240 --> 00:48:00.640 align:middle line:84%
Other people would
be very heartfelt,

00:48:00.640 --> 00:48:02.830 align:middle line:84%
and they just feel their
way through all this stuff.

00:48:02.830 --> 00:48:05.290 align:middle line:84%
So it's all very,
very different,

00:48:05.290 --> 00:48:08.560 align:middle line:84%
except on the ground state it
has similarities, expansion,

00:48:08.560 --> 00:48:10.480 align:middle line:90%
bliss, love, these things.

00:48:10.480 --> 00:48:23.180 align:middle line:90%


00:48:23.180 --> 00:48:26.570 align:middle line:84%
>> How do I experience
that oneness?

00:48:26.570 --> 00:48:33.320 align:middle line:84%
It could be on a very quiet
subtle level of just feeling

00:48:33.320 --> 00:48:36.260 align:middle line:90%
at home and oneness.

00:48:36.260 --> 00:48:38.540 align:middle line:84%
It could also be
on a sensory level.

00:48:38.540 --> 00:48:42.770 align:middle line:84%
I'm an artist, and
so sometimes there's

00:48:42.770 --> 00:48:49.030 align:middle line:84%
some subtle kind of
visual components to this,

00:48:49.030 --> 00:48:53.620 align:middle line:84%
you could say, like, threads,
golden threads connecting

00:48:53.620 --> 00:49:04.570 align:middle line:84%
all of us or a transparency
or a sparkling of that

00:49:04.570 --> 00:49:11.000 align:middle line:84%
which is lively in me, also in
you, that lively bliss oneness.

00:49:11.000 --> 00:49:14.290 align:middle line:90%
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

00:49:14.290 --> 00:49:32.440 align:middle line:90%


00:49:32.440 --> 00:49:39.010 align:middle line:84%
It could also be on the
level of hearing as well.

00:49:39.010 --> 00:49:43.450 align:middle line:84%
In 1973, I started to have
an unusual experience that

00:49:43.450 --> 00:49:45.290 align:middle line:90%
completely caught me off guard.

00:49:45.290 --> 00:49:48.310 align:middle line:84%
I was just sitting
meditating, and I

00:49:48.310 --> 00:49:53.120 align:middle line:84%
heard these most glorious
sounds I'd never heard before.

00:49:53.120 --> 00:49:54.620 align:middle line:90%
I opened my eyes.

00:49:54.620 --> 00:49:55.690 align:middle line:90%
I looked around.

00:49:55.690 --> 00:49:57.460 align:middle line:90%
There wasn't a radio on.

00:49:57.460 --> 00:49:59.000 align:middle line:90%
I didn't have a TV.

00:49:59.000 --> 00:50:03.910 align:middle line:84%
There was no choir
outside my apartment.

00:50:03.910 --> 00:50:06.640 align:middle line:84%
So it wasn't coming
from outside.

00:50:06.640 --> 00:50:11.350 align:middle line:84%
And then I started to hear
it on a regular basis.

00:50:11.350 --> 00:50:17.640 align:middle line:84%
And it was clear to me it was
sounds of what I call veda.

00:50:17.640 --> 00:50:23.400 align:middle line:84%
To me, veda, that's, V-E-D-A,
it's pure knowledge flowing.

00:50:23.400 --> 00:50:27.200 align:middle line:90%
It's that oneness, that peace.

00:50:27.200 --> 00:50:30.050 align:middle line:90%
There's some movement there.

00:50:30.050 --> 00:50:33.740 align:middle line:84%
And when there's movement,
there's some sound created.

00:50:33.740 --> 00:50:40.010 align:middle line:84%
So you can think of it as the
sound of the laws of nature,

00:50:40.010 --> 00:50:44.520 align:middle line:84%
I would say the innate
sounds of life in creation.

00:50:44.520 --> 00:50:53.972 align:middle line:90%


00:50:53.972 --> 00:50:59.130 align:middle line:84%
>> I then began to experience
a fascination with objects,

00:50:59.130 --> 00:51:02.370 align:middle line:84%
and I noticed it first
with natural things, like,

00:51:02.370 --> 00:51:04.895 align:middle line:90%
plants or trees or flowers.

00:51:04.895 --> 00:51:06.270 align:middle line:84%
There's just
something about them

00:51:06.270 --> 00:51:09.580 align:middle line:84%
that caught my attention
more than usual.

00:51:09.580 --> 00:51:15.260 align:middle line:84%
And as I looked at them, it
was like I felt initially

00:51:15.260 --> 00:51:19.140 align:middle line:84%
that there was
something behind them

00:51:19.140 --> 00:51:22.080 align:middle line:84%
that I could just
have a vague sense of.

00:51:22.080 --> 00:51:24.840 align:middle line:84%
I didn't quite know what it
was, but I had to keep looking.

00:51:24.840 --> 00:51:30.560 align:middle line:10%
I had to keep looking because
my status at that time was, OK,

00:51:30.560 --> 00:51:35.010 align:middle line:10%
here is this unbounded
awareness that's simply present.

00:51:35.010 --> 00:51:39.245 align:middle line:84%
And then there's all this
other stuff, that's the world,

00:51:39.245 --> 00:51:41.560 align:middle line:84%
and those are things,
and those are people.

00:51:41.560 --> 00:51:43.805 align:middle line:90%
And I don't really know what--

00:51:43.805 --> 00:51:44.930 align:middle line:90%
nothing's really different.

00:51:44.930 --> 00:51:46.460 align:middle line:90%
They look the same.

00:51:46.460 --> 00:51:49.700 align:middle line:84%
So as I continued
to pay attention

00:51:49.700 --> 00:51:52.460 align:middle line:84%
to this drawing,
this magnetizing

00:51:52.460 --> 00:52:00.090 align:middle line:84%
quality behind the plant
or the flower, it got--

00:52:00.090 --> 00:52:03.110 align:middle line:84%
it's hard to describe it,
like, it became porous.

00:52:03.110 --> 00:52:06.140 align:middle line:84%
Like, there were little, tiny
holes forming everywhere,

00:52:06.140 --> 00:52:08.780 align:middle line:84%
and then something was
coming through those holes.

00:52:08.780 --> 00:52:12.350 align:middle line:84%
And that was when I
began to recognize,

00:52:12.350 --> 00:52:18.680 align:middle line:90%
oh, this is the self there.

00:52:18.680 --> 00:52:24.890 align:middle line:10%
And there was just the
prominent feature of perception

00:52:24.890 --> 00:52:31.850 align:middle line:10%
that whatever I was
experiencing its nature as self

00:52:31.850 --> 00:52:34.520 align:middle line:10%
was there in front of me first.

00:52:34.520 --> 00:52:37.070 align:middle line:90%
I recognized that first.

00:52:37.070 --> 00:52:40.520 align:middle line:84%
I was seeing everything with
this predominant quality

00:52:40.520 --> 00:52:44.645 align:middle line:84%
of self, but then all
of it became one thing.

00:52:44.645 --> 00:52:47.550 align:middle line:90%


00:52:47.550 --> 00:52:50.040 align:middle line:84%
And that's hard to
really describe.

00:52:50.040 --> 00:52:56.310 align:middle line:84%
And when that happened, then
perception also changed again.

00:52:56.310 --> 00:52:58.410 align:middle line:84%
There was like
some final merging

00:52:58.410 --> 00:53:03.080 align:middle line:84%
that took place where the
subject and the object

00:53:03.080 --> 00:53:05.510 align:middle line:90%
had just completely merged.

00:53:05.510 --> 00:53:09.200 align:middle line:84%
So there wasn't a subject
perceiving an object,

00:53:09.200 --> 00:53:10.820 align:middle line:84%
there wasn't a
sense of a subject

00:53:10.820 --> 00:53:11.910 align:middle line:90%
or a sense of an object.

00:53:11.910 --> 00:53:15.690 align:middle line:84%
There was just the
flow of experience,

00:53:15.690 --> 00:53:18.230 align:middle line:84%
and that was just
really, really nice.

00:53:18.230 --> 00:53:21.632 align:middle line:90%
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

00:53:21.632 --> 00:53:27.480 align:middle line:90%


00:53:27.480 --> 00:53:32.070 align:middle line:84%
It's like riding with the waves
on the ocean or something,

00:53:32.070 --> 00:53:34.900 align:middle line:90%
where you don't do anything.

00:53:34.900 --> 00:53:38.670 align:middle line:84%
It just you're just moving
and just experiencing that.

00:53:38.670 --> 00:53:41.445 align:middle line:84%
And that was how the
experience became.

00:53:41.445 --> 00:53:56.370 align:middle line:90%


00:53:56.370 --> 00:54:00.570 align:middle line:84%
That flowing of
experience had begun.

00:54:00.570 --> 00:54:04.770 align:middle line:84%
And once that began,
then time started

00:54:04.770 --> 00:54:12.565 align:middle line:84%
to disappear because that
flow is every moment.

00:54:12.565 --> 00:54:15.625 align:middle line:90%
It's the now.

00:54:15.625 --> 00:54:17.055 align:middle line:90%
There's no time.

00:54:17.055 --> 00:54:21.130 align:middle line:90%
It's an eternality of flow.

00:54:21.130 --> 00:54:24.270 align:middle line:84%
So I think, at least
in my experience,

00:54:24.270 --> 00:54:27.105 align:middle line:84%
timelessness was an
aspect of oneness.

00:54:27.105 --> 00:54:43.050 align:middle line:90%


00:54:43.050 --> 00:54:44.580 align:middle line:90%
Then that stabilized.

00:54:44.580 --> 00:54:46.890 align:middle line:90%
So that's the way I live.

00:54:46.890 --> 00:54:50.550 align:middle line:84%
And it has a quality
of spontaneity to it.

